                    </div>
                </section>
                <section>
                    <div class="question-box">
                        <p style="font-size:1.2em; margin:0;"><strong>Step 2:</strong> 156 − 128 = 28 → leftmost bit = 1</p>
                    </div>
                </section>
                <section>
                    <div class="question-box">
                        <p style="font-size:1.2em; margin:0;"><strong>Step 3:</strong> 28 fits 64 or 32? No → bits = 0 0</p>
                    </div>
                </section>
                <section>
                    <div class="question-box">
                        <p style="font-size:1.2em; margin:0;"><strong>Step 4:</strong> 28 fits 16 → remaining 12 → bit = 1</p>
                    </div>
                </section>
                <section>
                    <div class="question-box">
                        <p style="font-size:1.2em; margin:0;"><strong>Step 5:</strong> 12 fits 8 → remaining 4 → bit = 1</p>
                    </div>
                </section>
                <section>
                    <div class="question-box">
                        <p style="font-size:1.2em; margin:0;"><strong>Step 6:</strong> 4 fits 4 → remaining 0 → bit = 1</p>
                    </div>
                </section>
                <section>
                    <div class="question-box">
                        <p style="font-size:1.2em; margin:0;"><strong>Step 7:</strong> Remaining bits 2,1 = 0 0 → <strong>10011100<sub>2</sub></strong></p>
                    </div>
                </section>
                <section>
                    <div class="box-blue">
                        <p><strong>Check:</strong> 128 + 16 + 8 + 4 = 156</p>
