                    <div class="box-blue">
                        <p><strong>Check:</strong> (5 × 16) + 14 = 80 + 14 = 94</p>
                        <p class="small-text">Clarify: What if the quotient ≥ 16? Divide again.</p>
                    </div>
                </section>
            </section>

            <!-- 10. HEX: HEX -> DENARY -->
            <section>
                <h3>Hex → Denary</h3>
                <div class="cols">
                    <div class="box">
                        <p><strong>Question:</strong> What is <code>3C</code><sub>16</sub> in denary?</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="box-blue fragment">
                        <p><strong>Answer:</strong></p>
                        <p>(3 × 16) + (12 × 1) = 48 + 12 = <strong>60</strong></p>
                        <p class="small-text">C=12, D=13, E=14, F=15.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </section>

