                <h3>Clarify: Hex Understanding</h3>
                <div class="question-box">Why is hex preferred over binary for humans?</div>
                <div class="fragment box-blue">
                    <p><strong>Because</strong> it is shorter to read/write and maps cleanly to 4-bit groups, reducing mistakes.</p>
                </div>
            </section>

